      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh independence study — pressure rise and flow uniformity",
      "description": "Three mesh densities (2.1M, 5.4M, 11.2M cells) evaluated for grid convergence index (GCI < 2%) on pump head and outlet velocity profiles at design-point flow rate 4.5 L/min, 2500 RPM. GCI criterion met on fine mesh.",
      "outcome": "passed"
    },
    {
