    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 criteria. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates adequate credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions across the five COU flow-speed combinations. Relative hemolysis index predictions support comparative device assessment against predicate. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger linear stress-additivity precondition is considered broadly applicable and does not require further verification at this risk level. Overall credibility assessment outcome: Accepted.",
